{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act14side_level_act14side_04_beg","storyGroup":"act14side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act14side_level_act14side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BI-4","storyName":"立雪求道","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"三大家族共同参与的圣猎即将开始。大殿之中，大长老与恩雅思绪交错。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act14side/level_act14side_04_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act14side_04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["谢拉格平民A","谢拉格平民B","谢拉格贵族","魏斯","恩雅","雅儿","大长老","长老A","谢拉格平民C","谢拉格平民D"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"subtitle","text":"恩雅，我希望你能争取成为圣女。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":5},{"type":"subtitle","text":"——为什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":6},{"type":"subtitle","text":"喀兰贸易如果想要在谢拉格更进一步，需要一个圣女，这是一个绝佳的机会。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":7},{"type":"subtitle","text":"——为什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"当然，事情不会这么简单。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"另两家人会有什么盘算你我都很清楚。但是我相信你若是被雪水滴中，一定能够通过考验，成为圣女。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"恩雅，我知道你可以做到。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"——如果我不想呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"——如果我失败了呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","text":"所有的反驳和疑问，我一句都没有说出口。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"因为我知道他会怎么回答，他一定会说。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":17},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_tinnitus","volume":"1","id":18},{"type":"subtitle","text":"你姓希瓦艾什，恩雅。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","id":20},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":24},{"type":"character","id":25},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_bg_24_g9_manoravenue.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":27},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkalley_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_longmendarkalley_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":28,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_172_svrash_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":31},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":33},{"type":"character","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"1","fadetime":"1.5","id":35},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"]","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"亲爱的，你快出来看，那是恩希欧迪斯老爷吗？","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"怎么可能，明天就是上山圣猎的日子了，老爷这时候不准备给圣女的供奉，一早跑到领地来视察做什么？","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"......等等，这还真是恩希欧迪斯老爷！","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"我听说，最早人们进圣山是不许骑驮兽的。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"尤其是要去拜见圣女的人们，要从跨出自家门槛的第一步开始，双掌合十，眼不离地，低着头一路祈祷过去。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"你看老爷现在的样子，莫不是他想效仿传统？","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"是啊，是啊。我是听说过这种习俗，可老爷他......毕竟是老爷啊，竟然也要这么低着头一步一步走到圣山上面去。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"你在说什么呢，老爷也是耶拉冈德的子民啊，你难道也和佩尔罗契家的傻子一样，觉得他忘了本？","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"你在胡说什么，我哪有这个意思！","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"我只是替老爷担心。你又不是不知道，另外两家贪得无厌，老爷提出了把大权交给圣女，他们竟然还不太乐意。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"那两家嫉妒老爷带来的发展，连我们的铁路都炸了，听说是想把谢拉格封起来，然后两家一起把咱们给包了。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"他们怎么敢？在耶拉冈德的眼前动武，祂可是会动怒的。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"他们还有什么不敢？","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"今天老爷这么手无寸铁地徒步走在街道上，明天又是三家带兵在山中打猎，真不知道他们又能做出什么伤天害理的事情！","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民A","text":"哎呀，可不要说这种不吉利的话！耶拉冈德在上，请保佑老爷一路平安！","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_277_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民B","text":"耶拉冈德在上，请保佑老爷一路平安！","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_npc_277_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格贵族","text":"恩希欧迪斯老爷，没想到今日还能见到如您这样虔诚的上山参拜者！","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_272_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","name2":"avg_198_blackd_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏斯","text":"抱歉，帕莱老爷，我家主人因行大礼，必须一路虔诚祈祷，无法分心回应您。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_198_blackd_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏斯","text":"在下替老爷向您致以问候。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_198_blackd_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","name2":"avg_198_blackd_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格贵族","text":"无妨无妨，是我冒犯了。耶拉冈德在上，还请原谅我。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_272_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格贵族","text":"只不过从图里卡姆到圣山，路程遥远，我等领民将恩希欧迪斯老爷的举止看在眼里，难免忧心。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_272_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","name2":"avg_198_blackd_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏斯","text":"老爷早下定了决心，请不用为他担忧。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_198_blackd_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏斯","text":"我们这一队护卫也不会让老爷出任何意外。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_198_blackd_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","name2":"avg_198_blackd_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格贵族","text":"那就好，愿耶拉冈德赐福于希瓦艾什。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_272_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_272_1#1$1","name2":"avg_198_blackd_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏斯","text":"也愿耶拉冈德保佑您。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_198_blackd_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":80},{"type":"character","id":81},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_bg_24_g4_boudoir.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":84,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":86},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","focus":"1","fadetime":"1.5","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"总觉得，围猎还没有开始，野兽却已经在惊慌了。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"您啊，只是从这窗格向外望，怎么就知道野兽在惊慌了？","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"积雪在发出响动。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"这么说来，明天圣猎时，您可要小心脚下。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"......大长老到了。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"唉，我需要小心的麻烦事多着呢。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":100},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":101},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":103},{"type":"character","id":104},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_24_g3_mainhall.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":105},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":106},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_sjoyasorrow_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":107,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":109},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"恩雅，你可做好了准备？","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"行装与致辞，我都已准备好了。","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"请大长老放心，我已经不是第一次参与大典了。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"此次大典不同于往日。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我听说，恩希欧迪斯要来参拜耶拉冈德。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"他愿意在这种时候表示虔诚，是好事。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"希瓦艾什前段时间还从蔓珠院请了许多神像，添置给领地里没有供奉神像的人。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"恩希欧迪斯真的会一夜之间变得如此虔诚吗？","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"长老A","text":"圣女大人，虔诚与否由祂注视，由祂评判，我等不能妄下断言。","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"长老A","text":"但即使是那些不知耶拉冈德的蒙昧之人，一旦目视五彩极光，也会自然被感化，向祂祷告。","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"长老A","text":"由此来看，一夜之间变得虔信，反而是祂威能的展现。","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"不论恩希欧迪斯心中有什么想法，他的行为是无可非议的。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#7$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"既然他所作所为是在维护信仰，圣女大人就不必有所顾虑。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"谢拉格人终究要向千年的传统低头。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#7$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"但愿如此。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"除了恩希欧迪斯，另外两族的家主会和往常一样上山等候。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"既然你将作为圣女接受三族权力移交，要准备的绝不仅仅是一番得体的言辞。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"圣猎也好，大典也好，但凡你对待三家的态度稍有偏颇，人们立刻会将其解读为一家得势或失势的信号。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我明白手中圣铃之重，也考虑好了如何应对。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"只差一样，狩猎用的长弓，还请大长老允许我取用。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"恩雅，你熟读历任圣女的手札，应该清楚，圣女不必亲自参与狩猎。这副长弓，你可是打算在圣猎开始的仪式上用？","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"圣女虽然不必亲历狩猎，但要是亲自参与了，应该也不算对耶拉冈德不敬。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"千年来蔓珠院的传统一向如此，圣女大人，不可不顾身份。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"圣女大人须代耶拉冈德接受三族奉上的猎物，代耶拉冈德将食物带到大典赐予祂的子民。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"要是这猎物改为圣女大人亲手狩猎而来，成何体统？","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"另外，眼下也不是适合您游猎的季节。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"您说得对，千年来倒是从未有过三族将大权交还蔓珠院的先例。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"只是交权一事，本应为缓和之策，可这些日子以来，圣山下却频频爆发混乱，将要交归圣女的土地也被肆意毁坏。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"就好像，他们当真不怕触怒耶拉冈德。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"耶拉冈德的子民正需要圣女大人去平息祂的怒火，向祂展现人们千年不变的虔诚之心。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"或许耶拉冈德需要圣女去传达祂的怒火。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#3$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"......圣殿之上，切莫妄言。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#3$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"另外，“勤劳者必将掌权，懒惰者必将受苦”。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我虽然知道三族交权于圣女，并非要圣女掌握实权。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"但圣女要维护信仰的地位，就不能只是等待着三族奉上结果，这并不是要展现他们的无能——而是我要首先做出表率。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"若要维护，就不可能谈什么改变。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_258_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","name2":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"耶拉冈德的子民已经向前走了，他们向祂祈祷的东西一定与千年前不同。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"祂也一定，无法做出与千年前相同的回应。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_174_slbell_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":176},{"type":"character","id":177},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_bg_24_g7_thoroughfare.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$sacrifice_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_bat_sacrifice_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":180,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":182},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_278_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"我听说老爷清晨从希瓦艾什家的老宅子出发，一路靠双脚走到这里，还没有休息过，连一口水也没喝上。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"爸，咱们给老爷送碗水去吧。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_278_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民D","text":"真要遵照传统的话，老爷这一路，确实要不吃不喝，不眠不休。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8b/Avg_avg_npc_278_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_278_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"可......已经一天了，爸。去圣山的路程，到我们这镇上才刚过半。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"而且前面出了镇子，天也要黑了，雪原上不知道会有什么危险。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_278_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民D","text":"啊，老爷来了......","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8b/Avg_avg_npc_278_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":193},{"type":"character","id":194},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","volume":"1","id":195},{"type":"text","text":"黄昏的街道上，希瓦艾什的队伍沉默地走来。恩希欧迪斯低垂着头，双掌合十，无声地朝向远方的圣山祷告。","id":196},{"type":"text","text":"听到脚步声的人们好奇地从窗口探出头，或者走出房门站在街道两侧。","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_278_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"爸。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"要是不能给老爷送碗水喝......我想跟着他到圣山脚下。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谢拉格平民C","text":"老爷开工厂教我技术的时候，我就决定跟着他。现在老爷心诚，要去拜圣山，我更要跟着他。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"character","id":203},{"type":"text","text":"人们一言不发地站起身，走下楼去，跟在希瓦艾什家护卫队的后面，步入雪原。","id":204},{"type":"dialog","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":207},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":208},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bse","fadetime":"1","id":209},{"type":"character","id":210},{"type":"image","id":211}],"characters":["谢拉格平民A","谢拉格平民B","谢拉格贵族","魏斯","恩雅","雅儿","大长老","长老A","谢拉格平民C","谢拉格平民D"]}